## Important Notes

- **Owner Types**: Owners can be either Users or Service Principals
- **Minimum One Owner**: Applications must have at least one owner
- **Owner Object Type**: The `owner_object_type` attribute must be set correctly based on the owner type being assigned
- **Permissions**: Ensure the service principal has permissions to read both users and service principals when assigning owners

